{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bread, thyme and rosemary in mixing bowl, chop <b>10 sec\/speed 8<b> then transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place Parmesan in mixing bowl, grate <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b> then transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place onions, oil, garlic and sage in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <b>2 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add root vegetables, 50 g reserved grated Parmesan, cream, milk, salt and pepper then cook <b>25 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>. Meanwhile, preheat oven to 210°C.","Transfer root vegetable mixture to a baking dish, sprinkle with reserved breadcrumbs and remaining grated Parmesan then bake for 20-25 minutes (210°C) until golden and bubbling. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["80 g bread, torn in pieces","2 - 3 sprigs fresh thyme, leaves only, to taste","1 - 2 sprigs fresh rosemary, needles only, to taste","100 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","100 g onions, halved","30 g olive oil","2 - 3 garlic cloves, to taste","3 - 4 fresh sage leaves, to taste","1000 g mixed root vegetables (e.g. parsnips, swede, potato, beetroot), peeled, thinly sliced (2 mm)","300 g double cream","300 g milk","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt","2 pinches ground black pepper"]}],"id":"r265833","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-T-oHxH0yGbw\/XZVQOMWryiI\/AAAAAAAAc-0\/8AsHxBlidUsT8EMTVAzIM-WWAtjRuWKjgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Izva6D6ipqEU-0hV.png","title":"Root Vegetable Gratin","publishedAt":"2018-02-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"12.5 g","fat":"38.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"28.2 g","calories":"2184 kJ \/ 526 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking dish (approx. 30 cm x 20 cm), oven","hintsAndTricks":["Serve this gratin as a tasty side dish alongside roasted meats, or as an impressive vegetarian main.","While any combination of root vegetables will work well in this dish, using beetroot gives the gratin a wonderful ruby colour.","Slicing all the vegetables the same thickness helps to ensure they cook at the same time."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","6 portions"]}